### Model fitting {.unnumbered}

Fit BIP-BA data.


::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
params_bip_init <- list(
  mu = 1,
  K = 1,
  beta = 1,
  beta_edges = 1,
  lambda_new = 3.5
)

fit <- fit_hawkesNet(
      ev = sim$ev,
      params_init = params_bip_init,
      mark_type = "ba_bip"
    )
```

